1
00:00:26,100 --> 00:00:28,820
I'll let you know
when I get to Shen City.

2
00:00:29,820 --> 00:00:32,060
If there's anything you can't handle,

3
00:00:33,020 --> 00:00:34,700
don't carry it all by yourself.

4
00:00:43,220 --> 00:00:44,340
Wait for me.

5
00:00:44,700 --> 00:00:45,620
Alright.

6
00:00:56,100 --> 00:00:57,460
Text me when you land.

7
00:00:59,180 --> 00:01:00,100
I'm off.

8
00:01:30,240 --> 00:01:36,080
=Echoes of Gang City=

9
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:41,040
=Episode 22=
(I Will Always Stand by Him)

10
00:01:42,860 --> 00:01:44,739
Raymond has gone too far.

11
00:01:44,740 --> 00:01:46,259
Seventy-two hours.

12
00:01:46,260 --> 00:01:48,939
Even if you rush back to headquarters
and do all you can to keep Spark running,

13
00:01:48,940 --> 00:01:50,700
it might not be enough.

14
00:01:51,380 --> 00:01:52,739
What about the legal side?

15
00:01:52,740 --> 00:01:54,100
Can it move any faster?

16
00:01:54,220 --> 00:01:55,059
My dad

17
00:01:55,060 --> 00:01:57,539
has already taken the highest-level team
to handle it.

18
00:01:57,540 --> 00:01:58,619
Even so,

19
00:01:58,620 --> 00:02:01,300
we need to be ready for a long fight.

20
00:02:06,140 --> 00:02:07,740
You can't face this alone.

21
00:02:08,420 --> 00:02:10,459
We can ask for help from Mr. Xu.

22
00:02:10,460 --> 00:02:11,860
With his influence,

23
00:02:12,180 --> 00:02:15,060
he might be able
to secure some resources

24
00:02:16,140 --> 00:02:17,179
for us.

25
00:02:17,180 --> 00:02:19,140
We're not at the point
where we need to trouble him yet.

26
00:02:19,740 --> 00:02:21,860
Let's not worry him for now.

27
00:02:25,180 --> 00:02:27,019
Put all available funds in the company

28
00:02:27,020 --> 00:02:28,379
into this.

29
00:02:28,380 --> 00:02:31,139
If it's not enough, I'll mortgage
my personal assets and shares.

30
00:02:31,140 --> 00:02:32,980
No matter what,
we have to keep Spark running.

31
00:02:33,260 --> 00:02:34,380
Okay.

32
00:02:34,980 --> 00:02:37,460
We've gotten through so much before.

33
00:02:37,540 --> 00:02:40,180
If you need money or connections,
leave it to me.

34
00:02:42,340 --> 00:02:43,460
Okay.

35
00:02:44,340 --> 00:02:45,660
I'll take care of everything
in Gang City.

36
00:02:45,860 --> 00:02:47,780
When everything is done,
I'll meet you in Shen City.

37
00:02:48,660 --> 00:02:50,220
I'll wait for you there.

38
00:03:19,140 --> 00:03:20,020
Hello?

39
00:03:20,100 --> 00:03:21,260
What's wrong?

40
00:03:21,820 --> 00:03:23,700
You miss me after just one day?

41
00:03:24,540 --> 00:03:26,500
Can you check

42
00:03:26,860 --> 00:03:28,860
what's been going on
with Yinghai Group recently?

43
00:03:30,140 --> 00:03:31,380
Yinghai Group?

44
00:03:31,820 --> 00:03:32,860
What's going on?

45
00:03:33,540 --> 00:03:34,900
Shen Gu said

46
00:03:35,340 --> 00:03:37,860
they've stopped supplying Qingniao.

47
00:03:38,460 --> 00:03:40,140
He has rushed to Shen City.

48
00:03:40,660 --> 00:03:41,980
I feel like

49
00:03:43,340 --> 00:03:45,060
it's pretty serious.

50
00:03:46,260 --> 00:03:47,380
I'm

51
00:03:47,540 --> 00:03:48,980
worried.

52
00:03:50,340 --> 00:03:51,139
Got it.

53
00:03:51,140 --> 00:03:52,139
Don't worry.

54
00:03:52,140 --> 00:03:53,500
I'll look into it.

55
00:03:53,860 --> 00:03:55,340
I'll wait for your update.

56
00:03:55,540 --> 00:03:56,660
Give me the phone.

57
00:04:12,940 --> 00:04:14,060
Boss,

58
00:04:14,380 --> 00:04:15,940
we're about to arrive in Shen City.

59
00:04:34,780 --> 00:04:36,339
(Shen Gu)
(I've landed.)

60
00:04:36,340 --> 00:04:37,860
(Rest up early.)

61
00:04:39,300 --> 00:04:40,219
(Xu Wanxin)
(Good night.)

62
00:04:40,220 --> 00:04:42,500
(Take care of yourself.)

63
00:05:01,140 --> 00:05:03,500
Compliance review? Nonsense.

64
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:05,819
They saw our Spark system

65
00:05:05,820 --> 00:05:08,059
as a threat to Raymond's monopoly,

66
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:09,739
so they're using
our upstream supplier, Yinghai Group,

67
00:05:09,740 --> 00:05:11,580
to choke us.

68
00:05:16,420 --> 00:05:17,540
Mr. Gu.

69
00:05:18,180 --> 00:05:20,140
Mr. Shen.

70
00:05:20,340 --> 00:05:21,540
When will Rachel arrive?

71
00:05:22,580 --> 00:05:25,579
Rachel and the rest have been held up
at customs overseas,

72
00:05:25,580 --> 00:05:27,419
but Lawyer Fang is handling it now.

73
00:05:27,420 --> 00:05:29,500
We're short on computing resources.

74
00:05:30,380 --> 00:05:31,339
On my way here,

75
00:05:31,340 --> 00:05:33,139
I asked Lawyer Fang

76
00:05:33,140 --> 00:05:34,500
to borrow computing equipment
from our partners.

77
00:05:34,540 --> 00:05:35,139
Raymond's people

78
00:05:35,140 --> 00:05:36,939
are launching attacks on Spark

79
00:05:36,940 --> 00:05:38,780
to drain our existing computing power.

80
00:05:39,060 --> 00:05:41,819
At this rate,
our drug simulation research,

81
00:05:41,820 --> 00:05:43,139
climate modeling predictions,

82
00:05:43,140 --> 00:05:45,739
and other projects will start
shutting down within 24 hours.

83
00:05:45,740 --> 00:05:47,539
This will impact our key partnerships

84
00:05:47,540 --> 00:05:49,300
and multiple international projects.

85
00:05:49,340 --> 00:05:51,339
Not to mention daily losses,

86
00:05:51,340 --> 00:05:53,780
they'll also use this chance
to take over our market share.

87
00:05:56,980 --> 00:05:58,100
Everyone,

88
00:05:58,980 --> 00:06:01,180
I'll personally lead the team

89
00:06:01,340 --> 00:06:03,060
to deal with the attacks on Spark.

90
00:06:13,540 --> 00:06:14,660
Everyone,

91
00:06:15,060 --> 00:06:18,340
this is Qingniao Group's contract
for borrowing computing resources.

92
00:06:18,740 --> 00:06:19,339
Of course,

93
00:06:19,340 --> 00:06:22,380
we'll cover all your losses
during this period.

94
00:06:22,740 --> 00:06:24,219
We can lend you

95
00:06:24,220 --> 00:06:25,540
our backup equipment.

96
00:06:25,660 --> 00:06:27,139
But if even a company like yours

97
00:06:27,140 --> 00:06:28,539
can be cut off indefinitely,

98
00:06:28,540 --> 00:06:30,740
then if the same happens to us,

99
00:06:31,180 --> 00:06:32,940
we can't bear the risk.

100
00:06:33,140 --> 00:06:34,379
Also, we've heard

101
00:06:34,380 --> 00:06:35,819
your core tech team

102
00:06:35,820 --> 00:06:37,859
has been held at customs.

103
00:06:37,860 --> 00:06:40,260
Even if we lend you the equipment now,

104
00:06:40,860 --> 00:06:43,859
can you solve the problem

105
00:06:43,860 --> 00:06:45,260
within a week as promised?

106
00:06:48,140 --> 00:06:49,140
Mr. Fang,

107
00:06:49,260 --> 00:06:52,419
we're grateful for Mr. Shen's

108
00:06:52,420 --> 00:06:54,939
financial support
and technical guidance in the past.

109
00:06:54,940 --> 00:06:58,380
But rather than
risking everything together,

110
00:06:58,740 --> 00:07:02,500
it's safer to preserve what we have.

111
00:07:13,380 --> 00:07:14,500
In that case,

112
00:07:15,260 --> 00:07:19,060
to ensure your operations remain stable,

113
00:07:19,140 --> 00:07:21,059
the guaranteed funds
mentioned in the contract

114
00:07:21,060 --> 00:07:23,460
will be transferred to your accounts
in advance.

115
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:25,099
I understand

116
00:07:25,100 --> 00:07:28,739
your concerns.

117
00:07:28,740 --> 00:07:30,780
But please don't worry.

118
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:33,659
Mr. Shen didn't offer you help

119
00:07:33,660 --> 00:07:36,540
just so he could ask for your help now,

120
00:07:36,860 --> 00:07:39,860
but to help everyone grow together.

121
00:07:40,580 --> 00:07:41,059
Of course,

122
00:07:41,060 --> 00:07:43,340
I'm not trying to guilt-trip you.

123
00:07:43,740 --> 00:07:46,539
You can review the contract

124
00:07:46,540 --> 00:07:47,740
and think it over.

125
00:07:47,820 --> 00:07:50,060
Feel free to reach out anytime.

126
00:07:51,220 --> 00:07:52,340
Alright.

127
00:08:00,540 --> 00:08:01,660
Bye.

128
00:08:14,420 --> 00:08:15,139
Did you find anything?

129
00:08:15,140 --> 00:08:16,460
Yes.

130
00:08:16,660 --> 00:08:18,419
Raymond Group joined forces
with nine companies

131
00:08:18,420 --> 00:08:20,339
to pressure Yinghai Group,

132
00:08:20,340 --> 00:08:23,180
which led to Qingniao
being cut off indefinitely.

133
00:08:23,740 --> 00:08:26,539
The Spark system,
which Qingniao invested heavily in,

134
00:08:26,540 --> 00:08:28,019
is now at risk of shutting down.

135
00:08:28,020 --> 00:08:29,140
Besides,

136
00:08:29,620 --> 00:08:32,259
the public opinion attacks on Minghui

137
00:08:32,260 --> 00:08:33,859
and the supply chain issues
done by Shen Tingyuan,

138
00:08:33,860 --> 00:08:36,339
Raymond was behind all of it.

139
00:08:36,340 --> 00:08:38,060
The key issue right now is

140
00:08:38,140 --> 00:08:40,379
Qingniao's core tech team

141
00:08:40,380 --> 00:08:42,260
being held at customs.

142
00:08:42,780 --> 00:08:46,260
Looks like Shen Gu
is under huge pressure.

143
00:08:48,740 --> 00:08:49,860
Where are you?

144
00:08:51,060 --> 00:08:52,180
I'm at Qingniao.

145
00:08:53,540 --> 00:08:54,660
I'm coming over.

146
00:08:55,020 --> 00:08:56,140
Mm.

147
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,700
Hello, Shen Gu?

148
00:09:06,380 --> 00:09:08,779
It'll take some more time
to find equipment resources.

149
00:09:08,780 --> 00:09:11,659
The embassy is already
assisting with negotiations.

150
00:09:11,660 --> 00:09:13,659
A private jet is on standby
at all times.

151
00:09:13,660 --> 00:09:16,860
I'll do everything I can
to get Rachel to Shen City.

152
00:09:17,340 --> 00:09:18,460
Understood.

153
00:09:24,180 --> 00:09:25,900
What brings you here, Wanxin?

154
00:09:28,420 --> 00:09:29,700
I came to check on you guys.

155
00:09:32,060 --> 00:09:33,180
Well.

156
00:09:33,940 --> 00:09:35,460
Let's talk in the office.

157
00:09:43,420 --> 00:09:44,540
Thank you.

158
00:09:47,820 --> 00:09:48,940
Lawyer Fang,

159
00:09:50,220 --> 00:09:52,780
I know Qingniao's situation is bad,

160
00:09:54,060 --> 00:09:56,460
but I need to know the truth.

161
00:10:07,740 --> 00:10:08,980
I want to help him.

162
00:10:14,860 --> 00:10:16,780
The situation is

163
00:10:18,140 --> 00:10:22,260
that Yinghai's supply cut
has already taken effect.

164
00:10:22,580 --> 00:10:24,060
Our current stock

165
00:10:24,220 --> 00:10:27,900
can only support core operations
at low capacity for three days.

166
00:10:29,140 --> 00:10:30,780
The lawsuit against Yinghai

167
00:10:31,460 --> 00:10:32,940
will take at least three months.

168
00:10:33,420 --> 00:10:34,259
And

169
00:10:34,260 --> 00:10:37,660
other companies don't trust
or share their resources

170
00:10:37,740 --> 00:10:38,900
with us.

171
00:10:39,660 --> 00:10:41,660
They're afraid
of taking on the same risk.

172
00:10:42,260 --> 00:10:44,979
So, as long as you secure resources,

173
00:10:44,980 --> 00:10:46,780
everything else can be resolved too?

174
00:10:47,620 --> 00:10:48,740
Exactly.

175
00:10:58,860 --> 00:11:00,940
Shen Gu hasn't been
in a good state lately.

176
00:11:04,660 --> 00:11:06,500
Did you know

177
00:11:06,860 --> 00:11:08,060
he's been taking medication?

178
00:11:10,620 --> 00:11:11,820
Medication?

179
00:11:13,340 --> 00:11:14,420
Cold medicine?

180
00:11:20,420 --> 00:11:22,980
Lawyer Fang, I saw it.

181
00:11:23,940 --> 00:11:25,900
When did this start?

182
00:11:28,380 --> 00:11:29,580
You know something about it.

183
00:11:31,980 --> 00:11:34,300
There were signs when we first met.

184
00:11:36,180 --> 00:11:38,420
But it wasn't serious.

185
00:11:39,420 --> 00:11:40,580
Later,

186
00:11:40,940 --> 00:11:43,500
when Qingniao just
started picking up,

187
00:11:45,660 --> 00:11:47,060
it got worse.

188
00:11:48,380 --> 00:11:50,260
But if Qingniao was improving,

189
00:11:51,660 --> 00:11:53,700
why did his condition get worse?

190
00:11:56,940 --> 00:11:58,260
Gu!

191
00:11:59,540 --> 00:12:01,179
We secured funding!

192
00:12:01,180 --> 00:12:03,379
Qingniao is on track now.

193
00:12:03,380 --> 00:12:05,860
All your dreams are about to come true.

194
00:12:09,340 --> 00:12:10,660
What's wrong?

195
00:12:10,940 --> 00:12:12,460
Too happy?

196
00:12:14,020 --> 00:12:15,140
You're standing in the rain?

197
00:12:15,540 --> 00:12:17,060
I'll stand with you.

198
00:12:18,980 --> 00:12:20,700
From today on,

199
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:24,260
we're a rising tech force
that can rival Raymond Group.

200
00:12:28,980 --> 00:12:30,580
Xu Wanxin got engaged.

201
00:12:38,820 --> 00:12:41,180
Everything is over

202
00:12:42,860 --> 00:12:44,700
before I go back to Gang City
to see her.

203
00:12:54,540 --> 00:13:00,340
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

204
00:13:01,620 --> 00:13:07,420
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

205
00:13:08,140 --> 00:13:13,059
♪You turn and look back at me♪

206
00:13:13,060 --> 00:13:14,779
I understand your engagement
to Shen Hao,

207
00:13:14,780 --> 00:13:17,340
and I know Minghui's situation.

208
00:13:17,740 --> 00:13:19,860
So I hope you'll break off
the engagement

209
00:13:20,260 --> 00:13:21,740
and choose to work with me.

210
00:13:23,340 --> 00:13:25,499
I call upon all persons here present

211
00:13:25,500 --> 00:13:27,459
to witness that I,

212
00:13:27,460 --> 00:13:31,139
Shen Gu, take thee, Xu Wanxin,

213
00:13:31,140 --> 00:13:33,339
to be my lawful wedded wife.

214
00:13:33,340 --> 00:13:35,059
(Gang City Marriage Registry)

215
00:13:35,060 --> 00:13:36,180
- I do.
- I do.

216
00:13:40,980 --> 00:13:44,619
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

217
00:13:44,620 --> 00:13:45,940
At that time,

218
00:13:46,460 --> 00:13:48,380
he was under constant pressure.

219
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:51,419
You know what happened to his family.

220
00:13:51,420 --> 00:13:52,660
Also,

221
00:13:54,260 --> 00:13:55,620
his regrets about you.

222
00:13:56,660 --> 00:13:58,380
All of that contributed to his illness.

223
00:13:58,660 --> 00:14:00,620
But long-term medication

224
00:14:01,060 --> 00:14:03,780
can cause irreversible damage
to the brain.

225
00:14:04,300 --> 00:14:07,660
That's a huge blow
for someone in his field.

226
00:14:08,420 --> 00:14:09,659
So he kept finding ways

227
00:14:09,660 --> 00:14:12,340
to stay in control.

228
00:14:12,700 --> 00:14:14,420
Can it only be managed with medication?

229
00:14:16,140 --> 00:14:17,260
Wanxin,

230
00:14:18,420 --> 00:14:22,340
you underestimate
how important you are to him.

231
00:14:23,460 --> 00:14:24,340
You

232
00:14:25,420 --> 00:14:27,180
are his best cure.

233
00:14:30,460 --> 00:14:31,940
But at a time like this,

234
00:14:33,820 --> 00:14:35,540
I'm not by his side.

235
00:14:38,900 --> 00:14:40,380
He doesn't want you to worry.

236
00:14:42,820 --> 00:14:44,340
More than that,

237
00:14:45,420 --> 00:14:47,420
I wish he would trust

238
00:14:49,340 --> 00:14:51,420
that I'll always stand by him.

239
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:05,479
(Gang City Financial News)

240
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:08,000
(Minghui Group)

241
00:15:35,050 --> 00:15:40,850
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

242
00:15:42,130 --> 00:15:47,930
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

243
00:15:48,650 --> 00:15:54,010
♪You turn and look back at me♪

244
00:15:55,130 --> 00:16:00,650
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

245
00:16:01,490 --> 00:16:07,130
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

246
00:16:08,410 --> 00:16:13,890
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

247
00:16:15,010 --> 00:16:20,330
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

248
00:16:21,490 --> 00:16:27,290
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

249
00:16:27,690 --> 00:16:34,650
♪How many letters have I written
just for you?♪

250
00:16:34,770 --> 00:16:40,450
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

251
00:16:41,130 --> 00:16:47,489
♪From this life on
no distance could keep us apart♪

252
00:16:47,490 --> 00:16:50,369
♪The promise we made♪

253
00:16:50,370 --> 00:16:54,049
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

254
00:16:54,050 --> 00:17:00,649
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

255
00:17:00,650 --> 00:17:07,050
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

256
00:17:07,450 --> 00:17:13,769
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

257
00:17:13,770 --> 00:17:18,890
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

258
00:17:19,370 --> 00:17:22,370
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪
